    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per institutional credibility plan. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model adequately predicts hemolysis index within 12.7% of experimental measurements across the full CPB operating envelope. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
